### Auth & Admin Bootstrap Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client (Humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@contentType = application/json
@adminKey = CHANGE_ME

### Create Admin User (HR bootstrap only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/admin
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-admin-api-key: {{adminKey}}

{
  "email": "admin@company.com",
  "password": "securePassword123",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "position": "HR Manager",
  "hireDate": "2022-01-01",
  "country": "France"
}

